{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":852281,"duration_api_ms":767883,"num_turns":104,"result":"## Sprint D Complete: Banner Notifications (V2-09)\n\n### What was implemented\n\n**`260302-03 StaffOrdersMobile RELEASE.jsx`** (v3.2.0, ~3940 lines)\n\n**BannerNotification component:**\n- Fixed position at top of viewport, z-60 (above header, detail view, modals)\n- Indigo-600 background, rounded-xl, Bell icon + text + dismiss button\n- Auto-hide after 5 seconds with fade-out animation (300ms)\n- Swipe-up to dismiss early (30px threshold)\n- Tap banner → navigates to relevant table card (closes detail view if open, scrolls to card, indigo highlight ring for 1.5s)\n- Non-blocking: `pointerEvents: 'none'` on outer wrapper, `'auto'` only on banner itself\n\n**Wired to polling cycle:**\n- Extended `pushNotify` with `bannerInfo` parameter\n- `buildBannerInfo()` function resolves order IDs to table names via `tableMap`\n- Single order: \"Стол 5: Новый заказ\" / \"Стол 5: Заказ готов\"\n- Multiple: \"3 новых заказа\" / \"2 заказа готовы\" (Russian pluralization)\n- Banner shows instead of toast for richer notification; toast used as fallback\n\n**OrderGroupCard changes:**\n- `data-group-id` attribute for scroll-to targeting\n- `isHighlighted` prop → `ring-2 ring-indigo-400` highlight with `transition-shadow`\n\n### Review findings (CC + Codex + correctness-reviewer)\n\n| Priority | Issue | Fix |\n|----------|-------|-----|\n| P0 | Nested setTimeout not cleaned up on unmount | Separate `autoHideTimer` + `dismissAnimTimer` refs with `clearTimers()` helper |\n| P1 | XSS surface in querySelector with groupId | `CSS.escape(String(groupId))` |\n| P1 | Inner timer in handleDismiss not tracked | Uses `dismissAnimTimer` ref |\n| P1 | handleTap inner timer not tracked | Uses `dismissAnimTimer` ref |\n\nAll 4 issues fixed.\n\n### Files updated\n- `pages/StaffOrdersMobile/260302-03 StaffOrdersMobile RELEASE.jsx` — Sprint D code\n- `pages/StaffOrdersMobile/BUGS.md` — Sprint D notes + review fixes\n- `pages/StaffOrdersMobile/StaffOrdersMobile README.md` — v3.2.0, component list, UX changelog\n\n### Git\nAll changes committed and pushed. Latest commit: `ce837ec`.","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"b47ca866-b67c-4a1e-863e-307c20ff5817","total_cost_usd":5.739682500000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":94,"cache_creation_input_tokens":127220,"cache_read_input_tokens":8174577,"output_tokens":29365,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":127220,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":94,"outputTokens":29365,"cacheReadInputTokens":8174577,"cacheCreationInputTokens":127220,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":5.617008500000001,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":18133,"outputTokens":7173,"cacheReadInputTokens":337835,"cacheCreationInputTokens":27914,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.12267400000000002,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Glob","tool_use_id":"toolu_01YVpQcA5uo5pry7R7LWwqeS","tool_input":{"pattern":"**/Design_WaiterScreen*","path":"C:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/002 Menu/Claude AI Cowork"}}],"uuid":"3814c2c3-102e-4e42-9be8-5fcfcff23f9d"}
